QuestData.Title: The Sunveil Excursion
QuestData.Description: Oh, right, I received a notification from someone a few days ago. The Reliquary, was it? They're looking for someone to... do something...$b$b<The Warlord rifles through some papers.>$b$bAh, here it is! Yes, Rohan Sunveil of The Reliquary is seeking able-bodied adventurers to assist with an archaeological expedition to the south.$b$bHere, take this with you. Why don't you go speak with that elf?
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Rohan Sunveil at the Sunveil Excursion in the Blasted Lands.
QuestData.RewardText: Welcome, traveler. Thank you for responding to my summons.
